05:43.920 --> 05:48.369
<i>...for capturing the manic Minotaur
of Manesly Manor.</i>

05:51.040 --> 05:54.362
<i>Shaggy, enough with the comics.
Pay attention. We're getting an award.</i>

05:56.960 --> 05:58.724
<i>Blue Falcon.</i>

05:58.880 --> 06:00.211
<i>And Dynomutt.</i>

06:03.720 --> 06:06.644
<i>Yeah, do you guys think
