<i>Well, it all started back in my childhood--</i>

06:33.360 --> 06:34.691
<i>Nope. No, we're good.</i>

06:34.840 --> 06:36.763
<i>Don't need to know why.</i>

06:36.920 --> 06:38.524
<i>Like, take him away, officers.</i>

06:39.480 --> 06:41.482
<i>Thanks for coming. Bye-bye.</i>

06:44.200 --> 06:46.601
