06:46.760 --> 06:49.081
<i>- And places to go.
- Let me guess.</i>

06:49.240 --> 06:52.847
<i>Does this have something to do with you
being a comic-book geek and a TV addict?</i>

06:53.000 --> 06:54.001
<i>Absolutely.</i>

