<i>Not a moment to lose, Dog Wonder.
Quick, to the Falcon's Lair.</i>

07:52.600 --> 07:54.523
<i>You got it, BF.</i>

07:56.120 --> 07:58.009
<i>Here we go.</i>

08:05.600 --> 08:08.683
<i>Dynomutt, to the Falconcar.</i>

08:09.360 --> 08:11.124
<i>Blue Falcon.</i>

08:11.280 --> 08:13.248
<i>And Dog Wonder.</i>

08:13.600 --> 08:16.126
<i>Away.</i>

08:16.280 --> 08:18.362
<i>The Blue Falcon is just so cool.</i>

08:18.520 --> 08:21.091
<i>Played to perfection
by the one and only...</i>

08:21.240 --> 08:22.685
<i>...Owen Garrison.</i>

08:22.960 --> 08:25.531
<i>And Dynomutt is so amazing.</i>

08:25.680 --> 08:28.081
<i>And our costumes are, like, groovy.</i>

08:28.320 --> 08:29.401
<i>High four.</i>

