08:55.880 --> 08:59.441
<i>We are going to win that costume contest,
buddy, old pal.</i>

09:03.160 --> 09:07.006
<i>I'm Dynomutt, Dog Wonder.</i>

09:18.360 --> 09:19.646
<i>I don't know, guys.</i>

09:19.800 --> 09:22.485
<i>That old Blue Falcon TV show
