09:29.120 --> 09:31.964
<i>...featuring mega movie star,
Brad Adams.</i>

09:32.120 --> 09:34.646
<i>He's cute
in a dark, brooding kind of way.</i>

09:34.800 --> 09:37.724
<i>But you know what's even cuter?
Littlest Fuzziest.</i>

09:37.880 --> 09:40.611
<i>They're only the cutest collectibles
