09:50.360 --> 09:51.407
<i>Please.</i>

09:51.560 --> 09:56.600
<i>Costume competitions, movie premieres,
obnoxiously cute collectibles. Ugh.</i>

09:56.760 --> 09:59.047
<i>I'm glad the convention
is supposed to be haunted...</i>

09:59.200 --> 10:01.089
<i>...by a horrible, mean, cruel monster-man.</i>

