10:14.680 --> 10:16.125
<i>But that's not happening.</i>

10:16.280 --> 10:18.203
<i>Nope. No way.</i>

10:19.320 --> 10:23.882
<i>You can use the laptop
after the convention. Hoo, hoo.</i>

10:24.600 --> 10:29.242
<i>Well, it looks like the world can rest easy
once again, Dynomutt.</i>

10:29.400 --> 10:30.890
<i>That's right, BF.</i>

10:31.040 --> 10:32.769
<i>And remember, kids...</i>

10:32.920 --> 10:37.209
<i>...it's the hero inside of you
that saves the day.</i>

10:39.960 --> 10:43.760
<i>Like, welcome to the Mega
Mondo Pop! Comic ConApalooza.</i>

10:43.920 --> 10:50.121
<i>The greatest collection of comic books,
TV shows, movies, everything.</i>

10:55.920 --> 10:58.366
