<i>I love it. I love it.</i>

11:09.240 --> 11:10.287
<i>Hmm?</i>

11:10.440 --> 11:15.321
<i>I can see the only mystery around here
is why I'm even at this Mondo geek-a-thon.</i>

11:24.120 --> 11:25.531
<i>That's right, folks.</i>

11:26.840 --> 11:31.721
<i>This is the new and improved Blue Falcon,
