01:06:34.200 --> 01:06:36.441
<i>One of them actually destroyed
the studio.</i>

01:06:50.280 --> 01:06:52.282
<i>So I was banned.</i>

01:06:52.440 --> 01:06:54.681
<i>Deprived of the one thing I loved...</i>

01:06:54.920 --> 01:06:58.367
<i>...making robots
who destroy other robots.</i>

