<i>...I finally came up with this brilliant plan.</i>

01:07:20.640 --> 01:07:23.644
<i>Using my knowledge of robots
and special effects...</i>

01:07:23.800 --> 01:07:25.643
<i>...I created Mr. Hyde.</i>

01:07:25.800 --> 01:07:29.850
