01:07:43.600 --> 01:07:45.682
<i>...in a master stroke of genius.</i>

01:07:45.840 --> 01:07:49.208
<i>So Mr. Garrison really was asleep
in there.</i>

01:07:49.360 --> 01:07:53.046
<i>But all this?
