01:10:14.680 --> 01:10:16.603
<i>I'm your father.</i>

01:10:18.040 --> 01:10:20.247
<i>And that means that Dynomutt
is actually...</i>

01:10:21.640 --> 01:10:22.846
<i>Scooby-Don.</i>

01:10:26.360 --> 01:10:29.091
<i>Like, old buddy, you are a real hero...</i>

01:10:29.240 --> 01:10:31.766
<i>...and a real movie star.</i>

